## 6. Migration Notes

### 6.1 Data Migration

No data migration required. In-memory conversation history is ephemeral and cleared on service restart.

### 6.2 Breaking Changes

No breaking changes in this release. Fully backward compatible.

* SSE stream format unchanged
* API request/response schema unchanged
* No new environment variables required
* No new dependencies added

### 6.3 Backward Compatibility

Fully backward compatible. The fix only changes internal ID handling logic. External API contract remains identical.

